      <section eId="sec_381_3">
        <num>381.3</num>
        <heading>Use of police records</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_381_3__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>to the respondent or his parent or person responsible for his\ncare; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_381_3__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>if the respondent is subsequently convicted of a crime, to a judge\nof the court in which he was convicted, unless such record has been\nsealed pursuant to section 375.1.\n  3. An order issued under subdivision two must be in writing.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
